{
  "texts": [
    "For example, Tambichik et al. [78] and Hussin et al.",
    "[79] observed a significant reduction in workability, with slump reductions of up to 43% and 40% at replacement levels of 30% and 15-30%, respectively.",
    "Similarly, Sumesh et al. [80] and Abdullah et al.",
    "[81] found that substituting cement with POFA at levels of 20% and 40% reduced workability by 25-30% and slightly increased the setting time by 5-10%.",
    "In line with these findings, Aziz et al. [82] reported a 15-20% decrease in workability as the amount of POFA increased, along with a slight rise in air content."
  ]
}